ercise is standalone reference data (filterable by ExerciseCategory)\n176\t- Article references many Articles via relatedArticleIds (N:N self-referential)\n177\t\n178\t## Screen to Entity Mapping\n179\t| Screen | Entities Consumed |\n180\t|--------|-------------------|\n181\t| Home | PregnancyProfile, WeightEntry (latest), MoodEntry (latest), Reminder (next), WeekContent (current week) |\n182\t| Cycle Tracking | CycleEntry, PregnancyProfile |\n183\t| Weight & Nutrition | WeightEntry, PregnancyProfile, WeekContent (nutrition tips) |\n184\t| Pregnancy Progress | PregnancyProfile, WeekContent, SelfCareCheckState |\n185\t| Mindfulness | Exercise, MoodEntry (today) |\n186\t| Exercise Detail | Exercise |\n187\t| Health Log | DoctorVisit, SymptomEntry, Reminder |\n188\t| Mood & Wellness | MoodEntry, PregnancyProfile |\n189\t| Education | Article |\n190\t| Article Reader | Article |\n191\t| Settings | PregnancyProfile, UserPreferences |\n192\t\n193\t## Mock Data Requirements\n194\t- 1 PregnancyProfile (week 22, due date ~18 weeks out, name \"Mira\")\n195\t- 15-20 WeightEntries spanning weeks 15-22 (values ~56-59 kg, gradual increase)\n196\t- 3-5 CycleEntries (pre-pregnancy history)\n197\t- 10-14 MoodEntries spanning last 2 weeks (mood levels 2-5, energy levels 2-5)\n198\t- 5-8 SymptomEntries with varied types and severities\n199\t- 3-4 DoctorVisits with realistic summaries\n200\t- 4-6 Reminders (mix of done and pending, next checkup in 5 days)\n201\t- 42 WeekContent entries (one per pregnancy week, with size comparisons, body changes, baby development)\n202\t- 4 SelfCareCheckState items per day (prenatal vitamins, hydration, kegel exercises, gentle stretching)\n203\t- 10-15 Articles across all 4 topics\n204\t- 8-12 Exercises across all 3 categories (breathing, stretching, meditation)\n205\t- 1 UserPreferences with defaults (kg, all notifications on, reduced motion off)\n206\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2df53568-1fcc-4cd0-8db1-0e5f3301dc0f","uuid":"82144fff-